00:15:09.952 --> 00:15:12.160
Not to try to do too much.

00:15:12.608 --> 00:15:18.304
In daily devotions, in meeting with God, and not to miss the main thing.

00:15:18.880 --> 00:15:22.592
Our most pressing need is not to master the Bible.

00:15:23.040 --> 00:15:25.536
but to be mastered by God.

00:15:25.536 --> 00:15:26.784
In Christ.

00:15:26.752 --> 00:15:30.464
Through his word in a day's portion.

00:15:31.392 --> 00:15:32.640
For a lifetime.

00:15:33.248 --> 00:15:35.552
I said, Father, would you make it true for me today?

00:15:35.520 --> 00:15:37.632
And these dear brothers and sisters.

00:15:37.664 --> 00:15:41.632
Provide for us daily in Christ through your word.

00:15:42.272 --> 00:15:43.776
In Jesus' name we pray.

00:15:44.416 --> 00:15:45.376
Amen.
